            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJeremiah%202%3A31-4%3A18%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_2_31%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2231%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3Bmy%20people%2C%20listen%20to%20the%20words%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EHave%20I%20been%20like%20a%20desert%20to%20Israel%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EHave%20I%20been%20to%20them%20a%20land%20of%20darkness%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EWhy%20then%20do%20my%20people%20say%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BAt%20last%20we%20are%20free%20from%20God!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EWe%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20need%20him%20anymore!%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_2_32%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2232%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3EDoes%20a%20young%20woman%20forget%20her%20jewelry%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eor%20a%20bride%20her%20wedding%20dress%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EYet%20for%20years%20on%20end%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Emy%20people%20have%20forgotten%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_2_33%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2233%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BHow%20you%20plot%20and%20scheme%20to%20win%20your%20lovers.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EEven%20an%20experienced%20prostitute%20could%20learn%20from%20you!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_2_34%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2234%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E34%3C%2Fspan%3EYour%20clothing%20is%20stained%20with%20the%20blood%20of%20the%20innocent%20and%20the%20poor%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethough%20you%20didn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20catch%20them%20breaking%20into%20your%20houses!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_2_35%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2235%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E35%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20yet%20you%20say%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E%26%23x2018%3BI%20have%20done%20nothing%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ESurely%20God%20isn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20angry%20with%20me!%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EBut%20now%20I%20will%20punish%20you%20severely%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebecause%20you%20claim%20you%20have%20not%20sinned.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_2_36%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2236%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E36%3C%2Fspan%3EFirst%20here%2C%20then%20there%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eyou%20flit%20from%20one%20ally%20to%20another%20asking%20for%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EBut%20your%20new%20friends%20in%20Egypt%20will%20let%20you%20down%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ejust%20as%20Assyria%20did%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_2_37%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2237%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E37%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20despair%2C%20you%20will%20be%20led%20into%20exile%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewith%20your%20hands%20on%20your%20heads%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Efor%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20rejected%20the%20nations%20you%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThey%20will%20not%20help%20you%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_3_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIf%20a%20man%20divorces%20a%20woman%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20she%20goes%20and%20marries%20someone%20else%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ehe%20will%20not%20take%20her%20back%20again%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20that%20would%20surely%20corrupt%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EBut%20you%20have%20prostituted%20yourself%20with%20many%20lovers%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eso%20why%20are%20you%20trying%20to%20come%20back%20to%20me%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Esays%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_3_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BLook%20at%20the%20shrines%20on%20every%20hilltop.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EIs%20there%20any%20place%20you%20have%20not%20been%20defiled%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eby%20your%20adultery%20with%20other%20gods%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EYou%20sit%20like%20a%20prostitute%20beside%20the%20road%20waiting%20for%20a%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EYou%20sit%20alone%20like%20a%20nomad%20in%20the%20desert.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EYou%20have%20polluted%20the%20land%20with%20your%20prostitution%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20your%20wickedness.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_3_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22v